A '''sailor''' was any individual who worked aboard, or derived entertainment from, [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]]-going sailing vessels. The water world of [[Spira/Legends|Spira]] had many sailors among its residents who enjoyed sailing their [[Yacht (aquatic)/Legends|yachts]].<ref name="TSR">{{JournalCite|1|The Spira Regatta}}</ref> The term "sailor" was also used to describe a crewmember of a [[wind rider]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sevarcos II]] who was in charge of operating the sail.<ref name="FTGS">{{JournalCite|2|The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos}}</ref> The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] also referred to some of their [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Alliance Fleet]] personnel as "sailors." For instance, Rebel Sailors could be found throughout the corridors of several [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]].<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

